            Regional Insights
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Education Services Across <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Switzerland</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            School options and education quality vary significantly by region
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Zürich</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-100">Diverse International Schools & Top Universities</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    International School Options
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-7">
                    ZIS (Zurich International School), ISZL, Inter-Community School, Lyceum Alpinum. Strong IB programs, American, British curricula. Wide range of language programs including German immersion.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    Higher Education
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-7">
                    ETH Zurich (world-renowned technical university), University of Zurich, Zurich University of Applied Sciences. Excellent academic pathways for university-bound students.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-600 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                    Best For
                  </h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-7">
                    Corporate families, finance professionals, tech workers. Multilingual environment, excellent public transport access to schools, strong extracurricular programs.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Geneva</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-100">UN & Diplomatic Schools, International Curricula</p>
            </div>
